<subSubSection id="C36351D6FF82FF991B5E7F53FBA0FAD8" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BC6025DFF82FF991B5E7F53FBFFFAB0" blockId="4.[843,1494,1034,1387]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">
Under 
<treatmentCitation id="0AD8244CFF82FF991BEB7F53FA3AFB91" author="HASSLER, E." box="[960,1494,1034,1058]" page=")" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" year="1910">
<taxonomicName id="4C7979DEFF82FF991BEB7F53FA3AFB91" authority=", HASSLER (1910: 68)" authorityName=", HASSLER" authorityPageNumber="68" authorityYear="1910" box="[960,1494,1034,1058]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="marginatum" variety="praecox">
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991BEB7F53FB8EFB91" box="[960,1122,1034,1058]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">B. marginatum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991CBD7F53FB19FB91" box="[1174,1269,1034,1058]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">praecox,</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE87FACFF82FF991CD77F53FA3AFB91" author="HASSLER" box="[1276,1494,1034,1058]" firstAuthor="HASSLER" page="68" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" pagination="66 - 71" refId="ref6666" refString="HASSLER, E. (1910). Ex herbario Hassleriano: Novitates paraguarienses. V. Bombacaceae. Repert. Spec. Nov. Regni Veg. 8: 66 - 71." type="journal article" year="1910">HASSLER (1910: 68)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</treatmentCitation>
accommodated the new forms 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991C887F73FA3AFBF1" box="[1187,1494,1066,1090]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">
paraguayense, 
<taxonomicName id="4C7979DEFF82FF991D647F73FA23FBF1" box="[1359,1487,1066,1090]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="argentinum">argentinum</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991B537F13FC20FBD1" box="[888,972,1098,1122]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">fiebrigii</emphasis>
based on the presence of glabrous staminal tubes. However, he did not designate a 
<typeStatus id="54C2BCFFFF82FF991C957F33FACCFB31" box="[1214,1312,1130,1154]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">holotype</typeStatus>
for this variety. Types of the names of the three forms are 
<typeStatus id="54C2BCFFFF82FF991D017FD3FA61FB11" box="[1322,1421,1162,1186]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">syntypes</typeStatus>
of the variety. We choose the type of the 
<taxonomicName id="4C7979DEFF82FF991CEF7FF3FAB4FB71" box="[1220,1368,1194,1218]" form="fiebrigii" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" rank="form">
form 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991D2B7FF3FAB4FB71" box="[1280,1368,1194,1218]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">fiebrigii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
that allows a clear application of the name of this 
<taxonomicName id="4C7979DEFF82FF991CDC7F93FA55FB51" box="[1271,1465,1226,1250]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" rank="variety" variety="according">variety according</taxonomicName>
to Hassler’s concept.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BC6025DFF82FF991B5E7E4BFBA0FAD8" blockId="4.[843,1494,1034,1387]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">
The present 
<typeStatus id="54C2BCFFFF82FF991BD17E4BFBB0FA99" box="[1018,1116,1298,1322]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">lectotype</typeStatus>
, 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991C417E4BFB12FA99" box="[1130,1278,1298,1322]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">Fiebrig 5244,</emphasis>
is also the 
<typeStatus id="54C2BCFFFF82FF991D537E4BFA3AFA99" box="[1400,1494,1298,1322]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7979DEFF82FF991B437E6BFB94FAF9" box="[872,1144,1330,1354]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" form="fiebrigii" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="form" species="marginatum">
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991B437E6BFBEAFAF9" box="[872,1030,1330,1354]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">B. marginatum</emphasis>
f. 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991C097E6BFB94FAF9" box="[1058,1144,1330,1354]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">fiebrigii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the 
<typeStatus id="54C2BCFFFF82FF991CF97E6BFADFFAF9" box="[1234,1331,1330,1354]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7979DEFF82FF991D7D7E6BFBA9FAD8" authorityName=", HASSLER" authorityYear="1910" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="marginatum" subSpecies="meridionale">
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991D7D7E6BFC9FFAD8" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">B. marginatum</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B90DDE4FFF82FF991BEF7E0AFBA9FAD8" box="[964,1093,1363,1387]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">meridionale</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
